import React, { Component } from 'react'
import { Container, View, Text, Input, Button} from '../../components/atoms'
import "./styles.scss"

class Dashboard extends Component{

    render(){

        return(
            <Container className="login">
                <View className="login-content" direction="column">
                    <View margin="60px 0 0 0">
                        <Text>LOGIN</Text>
                    </View>
                    <View direction="column" margin="50px 0 0 0">
                        <Input placeholder="Email" bottom="20px" width="100%" height="45px"/>
                        <Input placeholder="Password" width="100%" height="45px"/>
                    </View>
                    <View flexValue="1" align="flex-end">
                        <Button variant="primary" height="45px" width="100%">LOGIN</Button>
                    </View>
                </View>
            </Container>
        )
    }
}


export default Dashboard
